### 创建评测集
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rag/eval/datasets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "spaceId": 1,
  "name": "RAG 检索增强评测集",
  "description": "用于比较 VECTOR_ONLY、KEYWORD_ONLY、HYBRID、HYBRID_RERANK 的检索效果"
}
### 添加评测case
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rag/eval/datasets/1/cases
Content-Type: application/json

{
"question": "异步向量化任务的作用是什么？",
"expectedAnswer": "异步向量化任务用于记录文档向量化过程中的任务状态、成功数量、失败数量、跳过数量、开始时间、结束时间和错误信息。",
"expectedChunkIds": [1, 2],
"expectedKeywords": ["异步向量化", "任务状态", "成功", "失败", "跳过"],
"difficulty": "easy"
}

### 偏向关键词问题
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rag/eval/datasets/1/cases
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "EmbeddingTaskService 是做什么的？",
  "expectedAnswer": "EmbeddingTaskService 用于管理异步向量化任务的创建、查询和状态更新。",
  "expectedChunkIds": [3],
  "expectedKeywords": ["EmbeddingTaskService", "异步", "任务", "状态"],
  "difficulty": "medium"
}

### 查询评测case
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rag/eval/datasets/1/cases

### 启动VECTOR_ONLY评测
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rag/eval/runs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "datasetId": 1,
  "runName": "vector-only-top5",
  "retrievalMode": "VECTOR_ONLY",
  "topK": 5,
  "candidateK": 20,
  "enableAnswerGeneration": false
}

### 启动HYBRID_RERANK评测
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rag/eval/runs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "datasetId": 1,
  "runName": "hybrid-rerank-top5",
  "retrievalMode": "HYBRID_RERANK",
  "topK": 5,
  "candidateK": 20,
  "vectorWeight": 0.6,
  "keywordWeight": 0.4,
  "enableAnswerGeneration": true
}

### 查询run汇总
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rag/eval/runs/1

### 查询每个 case 的结果
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rag/eval/runs/1/results

### Compare eval runs
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rag/eval/runs/compare
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "runIds": [1, 2, 3, 4]
}